   321→def fractional(value: NumberOrString) -> str:
   322→    """Convert to fractional number.
   323→
   324→    There will be some cases where one might not want to show ugly decimal places for
   325→    floats and decimals.
   326→
   327→    This function returns a human-readable fractional number in form of fractions and
   328→    mixed fractions.
   329→
   330→    Pass in a string, or a number or a float, and this function returns:
